<item>
            <title>[LU-5786] LFSCK 5: Skip orphan objects handling if failed to be verified during the first-stage scanning</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5786</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, the LFSCK will skip the orphans handling for failed servers. Such skipping grain is too large and not accurate. We will consider to record the failed objects during the first-stage scanning, and notify related servers to only skip orphans handling for those objects.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
